1)
Date: 24-Mar-2006
From: Goran Trajkovski < gtrajkovski@towson.edu >
Subject: CFP: AAAI Fall Symposium: Interaction and Emergent Phenomena in Societies of Agents 

2)
Date: 23-Mar-2006
From: Kathryn Remlinger < remlingk@gvsu.edu >
