Subject: Cambridge Italian Dialect Syntax Meeting 
 



Cambridge Italian Dialect Syntax Meeting 
Short Title: CIDSM 

Date: 21-Apr-2006 - 22-Apr-2006 
Location: Cambridge, United Kingdom 
Contact: Roberta D'Alessandro 
Contact Email: rd325@cam.ac.uk 
Meeting URL: http://www.mml.cam.ac.uk/italian/ 

Linguistic Field(s): Syntax 

Subject Language(s): Italian (ita)

Meeting Description: 

1st Cambridge Italian Dialect Syntax Meeting, University of Cambridge, April 21-22, 2006 

The CIDSM website is finally online. You can find the programme with
downloadable abstracts, and general information about the conference
at: http://www.mml.cam.ac.uk/italian/news/cidsm/default.html

We look forward to seeing you in Cambridge!

CIDSM Organising Committee





