1)
Date: 27-Mar-2006
From:  HR < hr@svox.com >
Subject: Computational Linguistics: Language Specialist, SVOX AG, Switzerland 

	
-------------------------Message 1 ---------------------------------- 
Date: Mon, 27 Mar 2006 08:44:43
From:  HR < hr@svox.com >
Subject: Computational Linguistics: Language Specialist, SVOX AG, Switzerland 
 

University or Organization: SVOX AG 
Job Rank: Language Specialist  
Specialty Areas: Applied Linguistics; Computational Linguistics; Phonetics;
Phonology 
Required Language(s): Danish (dan)
                      Korean (kor) 
                      Norwegian, Bokmål (nob) 


Description:

SVOX AG is a dynamic technology company specialized in text-to-speech. We
are seeking to temporarily (7 months) add to our language development team
several language specialists for Korean, Danish, and Norwegian. You will
create new language components for use with our state-of-the-art
text-to-speech engine.

We invite applications from language specialists that natively speak one or
more of the above mentioned languages. SVOX provides a varied position in
an international, fast-paced, results-oriented environment.

Tasks and Responsibilities:
- Development of language-specific components needed to analyze texts
(grammars, rule sets, lexicon evaluation and script-based adaption)
- Quality assessment and improvement of phonemic transcriptions
- Definition of accentuation and phrasing rules
- Preparation of text material for recordings
- Supervising the recordings
- Annotating the recordings and creating a speech database
- Testing and quality assessment of the integrated system

Qualifications and Required Skills:
- Native speaker of Korean, Danish, or Norwegian
- Masters degree in linguistics, computer science, or related field
- 1+ years experience in text-to-speech technology
- Interest in speech synthesis, prosody, and morpho-syntactic analysis of text
- Working knowledge of English
- Has a positive attitude and enjoys working in a team
- Programming and scripting skills are desirable
- Willingness to relocate to Zurich, Switzerland for 7 months

Start Dates are:
- Korean: as soon as possible
- Others: summer 2006
- Please check http://www.svox.com for latest status

To apply:
Please send a cover letter and your resume to hr@svox.com.


Address for Applications 

	HR 
	Baslerstrasse 30 
	Zurich CH-8048 
	Switzerland  

Application Deadline: Open until filled.

Contact Information

	HR 
	Email: hr@svox.com 
	Phone: +41 43 544 06 20 
	Website: http://www.svox.com





